{"tid":742942,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇Netflix個d紀錄片","createTime":"2018-07-15T04:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T03:18:36.000Z","uid":136932,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"b5992cfe656bc4c830cc2beadcb6f42b16cf26bd","tid":742942,"uid":136932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"本身睇左netflix成年，佢original劇大約睇過晒<br />\n<br />\n咁有日我唔知道係紀錄片嘅情況下，開左佢套 Evil Genius黎睇(個陣以為係暗黑版 Big Bang Theory<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n點知一睇完第一集，覺得好鬼吸引，然後一口氣追晒<br />\n<br />\n呢個紀錄片係講美國有單銀行炸彈劫案，<br />\n<br />\n個犯人身上面有個炸彈，佢拎到錢後出銀行個陣已經俾警察包圍<br />\n<br />\n佢本來都好冷靜，都已經投晒降，但係個炸彈除唔到出黎<br />\n<br />\n佢地對峙左一輪，個炸彈就爆炸，犯人當場炸死<br />\n<br />\n咁個紀錄片就一步步去講出個真相，例如兇手係邊個，佢地點解咁做，警察點樣察到etc... <br />\n<br />\n套野非常詳細仲可以搵到班幕後黑手做訪問，係鉅細無遺嘅紀錄<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人睇過？？<br />\n<br />\n另外有套差不多嘅叫做 making of murderer又係好睇到痴線"},{"pid":"4a836d42e8e305b346ea65baf09dcc3e8bfc449b","tid":742942,"uid":136932,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/130126_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F130126_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=72c57603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補返張poster"},{"pid":"bed02889cb7d4482624b0b262902bfa36e0e5495","tid":742942,"uid":10249,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"我勁鍾意睇netflix啲紀錄片 evil genius唔錯 <br />\n<br />\n介紹埋你睇呢幾套-<br />\n<br />\nMaking a murderer (黑警硬砌生豬肉 仲要砌完再砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nConfession Tape (黑警不誠實迫兩個後生仔坐一世監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nThe Keepers (啲神父正pk 搞左幾十個女學生 天主教團體為左名譽極力聯手黑警襟住件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nLongshot (呢套算係happy ending 但如果唔係個辯護律師屑而不捨搵到條片 個好爸爸就要坐一世冤獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"7d7d36b75ae86791fce98ba8a998369b6a485c42","tid":742942,"uid":136932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bed02889cb7d4482624b0b262902bfa36e0e5495","tid":742942,"uid":10249,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"我勁鍾意睇netflix啲紀錄片 evil genius唔錯 <br />\n<br />\n介紹埋你睇呢幾套-<br />\n<br />\nMaking a murderer (黑警硬砌生豬肉 仲要砌完再砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nConfession Tape (黑警不誠實迫兩個後生仔坐一世監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nThe Keepers (啲神父正pk 搞左幾十個女學生 天主教團體為左名譽極力聯手黑警襟住件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nLongshot (呢套算係happy ending 但如果唔係個辯護律師屑而不捨搵到條片 個好爸爸就要坐一世冤獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"making of murderer我有睇呀，係正呀。不過冷靜返d黎睇，其實佢都好可疑。 最正係單案仲審緊，好期待season 2<br />\n<br />\n另外有套冤獄嘅紀錄片叫 staircase, 你有冇睇？？<br />\n<br />\n我見個trailer同making of muderer差不多"},{"pid":"4eb194548c1fa95e05e73395b419c47f139409c4","tid":742942,"uid":80982,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:44:25.000Z","msg":"睇過你個個 以為好悶 點知又幾吸引"},{"pid":"1cb554fd1c6cd4b0e39210b427bd2e28333b77c7","tid":742942,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"Try dirty money"},{"pid":"a3b39163508dce0aff7f0bc05602906d827b561d","tid":742942,"uid":30006,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"非打手，Netflix 幾廿蚊個月真係無理由唔比<br />\n繼續睇垃圾tvb啦香港人"},{"pid":"efbdf2fd72abe893149cb9ce52af742326de1243","tid":742942,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl